I have never listen a new song till end at first Go. Never! 
I was lying on bed when i first time opened this video posted by coke studio on its launch and started listening headphones ON! 
It was first time i couldn’t turn it off or left it half way. Ali Saab gets better and better as every minute passes. So unreal voice, grip and control over rise and fall, that patience in letting the breathe collaborate with instruments and bloody being least bothered of how many will get addict to it even after 2 years. Such a favour this has done to this world. A therapy ! Period.
